'''[[electromagnetic]] [[spectrum]]'''

# The entire [[range]] of [[wavelengths]] of all known [[electromagnetic radiation]]s extending from [[gamma rays]] through [[visible light]], [[infrared]], and [[radio waves]], to [[X Rays]]. It is divided into 26 alphabetically designated [[bands]], having [[frequencies]] of 0 to at least 10<sup>23</sup> [[hertz]].

